title: (PSX-PSP) Lunar:Silver Star Story Complete converted properly (K
description:
LUNAR: SILVER STAR STORY COMPLETE

Return to the world of Lunar, in the completely reworked 32-bit version of the SEGA CD classic. Journey back to a place where dragons yet live, and magic is valued above all else. Join Alex, the young adventurer as he begins a quest with his friends to save their land from the crushing advance of the Magic Emperor. Explore dungeons, fight terrifying monsters, and gather information from the locals as you advance toward the explosive confrontation with the Magic Emperor himself!
